items.title: DeepSomatic, an open-source AI model, is speeding up genetic analysis for cancer research.
items.summary: DeepSomatic is a new AI tool that helps identify complex genetic variants in cancer cells . It's been created by Google and Microsoft . The tool is designed to identify genetic variants that can be traced to cancer cells using an algorithm that can identify a specific gene in a cancer cell to identify the cancer cells involved in the cancer process . It is the latest in a series of AI tools developed by Microsoft and Google .
